---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Adventures - Bradley Spillert">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="section-heading fade-in">Beyond the Desk</h1>

      <div class="fade-in space-y-10 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Running</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Training for a half marathon with my girlfriend. We run around Somerville and the Charles River most weeks. Still working on getting faster, but showing up is the hard part.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Skiing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Ikon Pass holder. Waterville Valley, Loon, Mount Snow, and wherever the snow is best that weekend. Made it out to Brighton Resort in Utah last season.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Scuba</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Advanced NAUI certified. There is something about being 80 feet underwater that completely resets your brain.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Hiking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Acadia is the go-to. Northeast trails mostly, with the occasional trip out west. AllTrails and Gaia GPS on every hike.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Dodgeball</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Volo Sports league in the city. Exactly as fun and chaotic as it sounds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Go-Kart Racing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            K1 Speed adult league. The fastest way to feel like a Formula 1 driver without any of the talent or money.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-white/[0.04]">
        <h2 class="text-white font-medium mb-4">Other things</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          3D printing (built my own CoreXY), electronics and PCB design, knife collecting, quilting and sewing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-white font-medium mb-3">On repeat</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Caamp, Mt. Joy, Rainbow Kitten Surprise, Band of Horses -- that kind of thing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
